{"tid":2039974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港版國安法】黑暴猖獗！","createTime":"2020-05-28T09:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T10:34:10.000Z","uid":293787,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad5dbac9fb390703450a1879603c50da104957e","tid":2039974,"uid":293787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【港版國安法】殼王旗下建築商保華 驚地盤物料被用作抗爭 限分判半句鐘處理</span><br />\n<br />\n有讀者報料，「殼王」陳國強持股的南岸集團（577）旗下的工程承建商保華建業向駱克道商業項目的分判商發備忘錄，內文形容「黑暴猖獗」，要求分判在吊運區卸貨後，貨物必須盡快送入地盤，以免「黑暴分子」將磚頭、喉通等物料作為與警察抗爭的武器。如果分判於吊運區卸貨後擺放超過半小時，即會當垃圾處理，而一切費用由分判承擔。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200527/ZKNU3EBKN7GDRND5ZAKY57F6UI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200527%2FZKNU3EBKN7GDRND5ZAKY57F6UI%2F&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=717c9a6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200527%2FZKNU3EBKN7GDRND5ZAKY57F6UI%2F&h=17e34079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200527/ZKNU3EBKN7GDRND5ZAKY57F6UI/</a>"},{"pid":"ca5bf870698b22841b66ee604448796e11db45d9","tid":2039974,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:01:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香 港 著 名 女 博 士 因 豐 滿 上 圍 引 來 陳 國 強 等 高 層 覬 覦 問 價</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/mw690/6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F6776b853gy1fka5xap6cqj20zk0qoaji.jpg&h=ee59598d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃博士身穿紅連身裙滿臉春光的回答高層首長問題"},{"pid":"708cae14e6f0cc21e439ed0221530f19eb42c55f","tid":2039974,"uid":293787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:25:02.000Z","msg":"一隻保華狗比負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"